author: The Math Navigator Family
message: Welcome! We are pleased to announce that our Math Navigator website is ready for use! With this website, you can check what available programs we have and even upcoming programs in the near future. To check out program details such as schedules and price, check out our classes by clicking on a Program in our Programs page. If you have any questions or any feedback (this website is still in beta-release), please contact us by using our Contact page. Thank you for being part of our community!
